

                    ====================================
                    Experimentation ground for using Goa
                    ====================================


This repository is Norman Feske's private playground used while developing and
testing the Goa tool.

:Article series about Goa on Genodians.org:

  [https://genodians.org/nfeske/index]

:Goa tool:

  [https://github.com/genodelabs/goa]


Example goarc
-------------

The following content is a useful starting point for a .goarc configuration
when working with the projects within this repository.

! # let Goa share the depot and public directories with Genode
! set depot_dir  /path/to/src/genode/depot
! set public_dir /path/to/src/genode/public
!
! # versions needed for using 'goa --run-as nfeske'
! set run_as nfeske
! set version(nfeske/pkg/drivers_interactive-linux)   2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/base-linux)                  2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/init)                        2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/linux_rtc_drv)               2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/nitpicker)                   2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/report_rom)                  2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/rom_filter)                  2023-04-25
!
! # created from Genode's source repositories
! set version(nfeske/src/sdl2)       2023-04-27
! set version(nfeske/api/sdl2)       2023-04-27
! set version(nfeske/src/mesa)       2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/black_hole) 2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/expat)      2023-01-23
! set version(nfeske/src/libdrm)     2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/vfs_gpu)    2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/lx_fs)      2023-04-25
! set version(nfeske/src/gnumake)    2023-04-30
!
! # versions of the projects within the goa-playground
! set version(nfeske/pkg/unix)          2023-06-16
! set version(nfeske/pkg/m68k-sdk)      2023-06-16
! set version(nfeske/src/binutils-m68k) 2023-06-16
! set version(nfeske/api/binutils-m68k) 2023-06-16

